Lob,Simple,Area,Mail,API,is,a,fee,based,cloud,API,that,allows,businesses,to,prospect,entire,delivery,areas,or,zip,codes,to,grow,customer,base,This,API,service,does,not,require,a,contract,allowing,single,or,recurring,mass,mailings,Lob,API,requires,an,authentication,key,for,the,creation,of,bulk,mailing,jobs,that,are,processed,and,mailed,This,API,provides,Ruby,Node,js,PHP,Java,Python,wrappers,for,ease,of,integration